skins.shipDescription: Type B1 cruiser submarine C I-26.
skins.selfIntroduction: Question! Which Sakura Empire submarine was the first to sink an Eagle Union merchant ship? You guessed it, this clever little cutie I-26 did! ... What happened after that, you ask? Let's leave the past behind us and focus on the present! *Giggle*
skins.acquisition: Submarine I-26 has arrived to be your roommate from now on! Hehehe~ Let me guess: you've really been looking forward to meeting me, right?
skins.login: Jumpity! ... Hehe~ Did I spook you, Commander?
skins.details: Tans are a sign of good health! So why not come with me and sunbathe a bit?
skins.secretaryIdle1: "What's up with my ears"? Hm? Do you wanna feel them?
skins.secretaryIdle2: Sorting paperwork... Ugh, so boring... Hey, why don't we play beach volleyball instead?
skins.secretaryIdle3: Maybe I should go for a swim~ Oh, I know! Commander, wanna have a swimming competition to see who's faster? Hehehe~
skins.secretaryTouch: Hm? Need any help doing your warm-ups?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: What are you fantasizing about? C'mon, tell me~ Hehehe~

skins.shipDescription: Many secrets lie at the bottom of the ocean! Commander, let's go looking for them next time! It'll be like a field trip~ Heheh!
skins.acquisition: Many secrets lie at the bottom of the ocean! Commander, let's go looking for them next time! It'll be like a field trip~ Heheh!
skins.login: Innsmouth! ... Hehe~ Did I spook you, Commander? Don't worry, this is just a stuffed toy!
skins.details: School's just boring compared to the ocean... Like, there's tons of undiscovered fish species and monsters down at the bottom of the ocean! I wish I could see how they look~
skins.secretaryIdle1: Big fish eat regular fish. Regular fish eat small fish. Hang on... what do small fish eat, again...?
skins.secretaryIdle2: If you were an anglerfish, you could work late at night without having to turn on the lights!
skins.secretaryIdle3: It's not easy to swim without a swimsuit~ Baww...
skins.secretaryTouch: You should give this anglerfish plushie a hug! It's really soft and cuddly!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Haven't I told you I'm not a fish?!

skins.shipDescription: Commander, are you also waiting for the fireworks to start? There's still some time, so let's have a little chat!
skins.acquisition: Commander, are you also waiting for the fireworks to start? There's still some time, so let's have a little chat!
skins.login: Commander, are you awake? You totally missed the fireworks! Ahaha... Just kidding! It's still early.
skins.details: Ugh... I always feel like there's something uncomfortable sticking out of my hair. Commander, can you help brush my hair?
skins.secretaryTouch: It's fine to take a nap if you'd like. I'll wake you up before the fireworks start.
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Eek! Commander, don't try to take advantage of the fact that I can't move around very well!
